text: Moreirense Futebol Clube is a Portuguese professional football club based in Moreira de Cónegos, Guimarães Municipality, in Minho. It was founded on 1 November 1938 and it plays in the Primeira Liga. ==Other websites== *Official website *Zerozero team profile Category:20th-century establishments in Portugal Category:1938 establishments in Europe Category:Portuguese football clubs Category:Braga District
